#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:5
msgid "策略思路"
msgstr "Strategy and Ideas"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:7
msgid "真实做市策略依赖逐笔盘口、挂撤单队列和成交优先级；"
msgstr ""
"Real market-making strategies rely on tick-by-tick order book, "
"order queues, and order priority."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:8
msgid ""
"qteasy 回测层是 Bar 级撮合抽象，本示例以“均值回归双边挂单”近似做市"
"行为；"
msgstr ""
"The qteasy backtesting layer is a Bar-level matching abstraction. "
"This example approximates market-making behavior with \"mean "
"regression bilateral order placement\"."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:9
msgid "当价格偏离均值上轨时卖出，偏离下轨时买入，中间区域观望。"
msgstr ""
"Sell when the price deviates from the upper band of the average, "
"buy when it deviates from the lower band, and observe in the "
"middle range."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:11
msgid "诚实说明"
msgstr "Honesty"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:13
msgid "本示例不是交易所级别的真实做市仿真；"
msgstr ""
"This example is not a real market-making simulation at the "
"exchange level;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_10_做市商交易.md:14
msgid ""
"仅用于讲解 qteasy 在高频风格场景下的 `VS` 信号和 stepwise 回测流"
"程。"
msgstr ""
"This is only intended to explain the `VS` signal and stepwise "
"backtesting process of qteasy in high-frequency style scenarios."

